- Saurian Spearwoman: Saurian Skirmisher alternative upgrade.
- Saurian Warden: Saurian Spearwoman upgrade.
- Saurian Seer: Saurian Soothsayer upgrade.
- Saurian Prophet: Saurian Oracle upgrade."
